      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-cnt-sts-imp-ric      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Flag di controllo status visualizzazione        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-cnt-sts-vis-ric      .
